author: Tom FitzGerald
title: Stanford defense puts clamps on Washington, 31-14
text:
Photo: Marcio Jose Sanchez, Associated Press Stanford running back Christian McCaffrey runs against Washington during the first half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, in Stanford, Calif. (AP Photo/Marcio Jose Sanchez) Stanford running back Christian McCaffrey runs against Washington...
Without clicking at the nearly point-a-minute pace of the previous two games, Stanford nevertheless trounced punchless Washington Saturday night.
